public class PdfCode32Barcode
extends PdfCode39Barcode

Represents a Code32 barcode. Only the following symbols are allowed in a Code 32 barcode: 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 0. The barcode length is 9 digits (8 user defined digits + 1 check digit). Code 32 barcodes are also known as Italian Pharmacode barcodes.
